headline: Bitcoin Prices Face Fresh Pressure

headline: Is It Worth Investing in Coinbase Global (COIN) Based on Wall Street's Bullish Views?
summary: The average brokerage recommendation (ABR) for Coinbase Global (COIN) is equivalent to a Buy. The overly optimistic recommendations of Wall Street analysts make the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric questionable. So, is it worth buying the stock?

headline: Bitcoin, XRP, Ethereum Dive. Why Cryptos Are Getting Bashed Again.
summary: The Bitcoin price was falling amid a recent selloff in Big Tech stocks and expectations that Kevin Warsh will be appointed the next chair of the Federal Reserve, which is dragging down cryptocurrencies.  Robinhood  a cryptocurrency exchange, fell by 0.3% and  Coinbase  fell by 2.7%.  At the same time, there are mounting expectations that Kevin Warsh will be nominated to replace Jerome Powell as head of the U.S. central bank.
